OL,3,CIn a US first, both parents of a
OL,4,Cschool shooter are found guilty of
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FThe father of a school shooter has
OL,8,Fbeen found guilty of involuntary
OL,9,Fmanslaughter, a second conviction
OL,10,Fagainst the teenager's parents who
OL,11,Fwere accused of failing to secure a
OL,12,Fgun at home and doing nothing to
OL,13,Faddress acute signs of mental health
OL,14,Fissues.
OL,16,FThe jury verdict on Thursday means
OL,17,FJames Crumbley has joined Jennifer
OL,18,FCrumbley as a cause of the killing of
OL,19,Ffour students at Oxford High School,
OL,20,FMichigan in 2021.
