OL,3,CIn a US first, both parents of a
OL,4,Cschool shooter are found guilty of
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,FThey had separate trials as the first
OL,8,FUS parents to be charged in a mass
OL,9,Fschool shooting committed by their
OL,10,Fchild.
OL,12,FMs Crumbley, 45, was convicted of
OL,13,Finvoluntary manslaughter in February.
OL,15,FOn the afternoon of November 30, 2021,
OL,16,FEthan Crumbley, now 17, was at school
OL,17,Fwhen he pulled the gun from his
OL,18,Fbackpack and shot ten students and a
OL,19,Fteacher, killing four of his peers.
