OL,7,FInvestigators found an empty gun case
OL,8,Fand empty ammunition box on the
OL,9,Fparents' bed. A cable that could have
OL,10,Flocked the gun was still in a package,
OL,11,Funopened.
OL,13,FEthan told a judge that the gun was
OL,14,Fnot locked when he stuffed it in his
OL,15,Fbackpack.
OL,17,FMr Crumbley's lawyers tried to
OL,18,Femphasise to jurors that he did not
OL,19,Fconsent to any gun access by his son.
