OL,3,CIn a US first, both parents of a
OL,4,Cschool shooter are found guilty of
OL,5,Cmanslaughter
OL,7,F"James Crumbley is not on trial for
OL,8,Fwhat his son did," prosecutors said,
OL,9,F"James Crumbley is on trial for what
OL,10,Fhe did and for what he didn't do."
OL,12,FAfter the verdict, defence attorney
OL,13,FMariell Lehman said Mr Crumbley
OL,14,F"obviously feels terrible" about what
OL,15,Fhappened at the school.
OL,17,FBoth Mr and Ms Crumbley face a
OL,18,Fpossible minimum sentence of as much
OL,19,Fas 10 years in prison when they return
OL,20,Fto court in April.
